title: Cuonzo Martin manages chemistry of deep Cal team
text:
Photo: Connor Radnovich, The Chronicle Head coach Cuonzo Martin explains a drill during Cal Bears men's basketball practice in Berkeley, California, on Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015. Head coach Cuonzo Martin explains a drill during Cal Bears men's...
Each Sunday morning, between breakfast and study hall, Cal men’s basketball players meet in their Haas Pavilion locker room to discuss matters greater than game plans.
